Strawberry matcha🍓🍵

Ingredients - 
Matcha - 5-6g 
Water - 50-60ml or oat milk 

Oat milk 
Oats (rolled) - 1/2 cup 
Water - 2 cup 
Vanilla - 1/2 tsp
Sweetener - 1-2 tsp 

Strawberry jam
strawberries - 1 cup 
Sweetener - 1 Tbsp 

You can also use any other milk and fresh strawberries.
